n_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"482b5ef653eec6379da2c680aca11ad6","url_token":"he-liao-shui-guo","name":"喝了水果","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-683d4546f075f2baeab5056040edca77_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-683d4546f075f2baeab5056040edca77_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/482b5ef653eec6379da2c680aca11ad6","user_type":"people","headline":"print（''hello，world！''）","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563701339","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546266905,"updated_time":1546329932,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e歌德作词，巴赫谱曲，一起歌颂他的智慧。清华北大双震撼，正负质数两开花\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e证伪，1在国际数学界不被看做质数，因此才有了现在欧拉形式的哥德巴赫猜想，就是题主所用的命题。这就等于循环论证，是错的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e循环论证\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e闹剧开头，闹剧收尾\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e两开花两开花，惹不起。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562957496,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562957496","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546166003,"updated_time":1546182224,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e为什么？为什么这种问题下还有人为题主洗白，鼓励少年追梦？为什么？为什么为什么？是我的价值观出了什么大问题了吗？哗众取众缺乏敬畏之心亦或是对自我能力的过高评价，也可以以梦想的崇高而带过吗？为什么为什么为什么？？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561741973,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561741973","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545995189,"updated_time":1545995189,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e今天上高代课的时候，高代老师讲的一个事例可以送给提问者\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大概在零几年的时候，有一个学长一入学就表示出了对此类问题的极高兴趣，然后就整天只研究数论方面的的问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且还说他证出来了让老师看是否正确，但老师说那只有一页纸的证明，他是看都不会看的，如果这么简单的话，那前面那么多大数学家是傻子吗？最后好像那位学长挂了许多专业课，并没有毕业。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e每年都有许多人声称自己证出了哥德巴赫猜想这类的，但是都是沉浸在自己的世界中不可自拔。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你还是个高中生，那我想说你的路还长，如果你真心喜爱数学，欢迎你报考数学专业，从最基础的数分高代学起，那你会了解到原来高中的数学知识不值一提。只有你不断向上攀登，你才能看到更加广阔的世界，而并不是现在山下看着山峰说：“这不是触手可及吗？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有清华北大到底对你意味着什么，是旁人提起的无限荣耀还是虚荣或者自身能力的肯定，那样的你并不适合专心于数学研究。清华北大只能意味着你有更好的教育平台，但是你的成就也只能由你来一步一步的完成，如果你真的喜爱数学，我相信就算是一个二本的大学也并不会阻止你进步的脚步。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不要过分在意别人的冷嘲热讽，人不轻狂枉少年，但是当下的你就是属于忍受不了正派的扎马步打基本功然后选择了走火入魔的一派人。你更应该做到的是提升自己的眼界和能力，17岁的你做不到，也许70岁的你就能做到呢？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561089033,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b30a3ab7684f2c6b395e7b4100a1cf12","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561089033","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545915356,"updated_time":1545915356,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主，如果你真是数学天才的话，我希望你好好学习奥林匹克竞赛，因为这个竞赛对于真的数学大神而言不算很难的（陶哲轩李开复等等）而且拿了省一，杀进夏令营就能保送个不错的学校了。能在奥林匹克国际比赛上拿奖，清华北大也不在话下了，而这些对于真的数学天才而言都不算很难。证明哥猜不妨暂停下来，试试奥赛，这样以后也更有机会接触到更多数学天才来一起讨论哥猜这种问题……\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561049476,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b2380a63354baa1686320b7e666987be","url_token":"qian-ming-xi-85","name":"钱明晰","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b2380a63354baa1686320b7e666987be","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561049476","thumbnail